Welcome to /r/Anuradhapura

A subreddit for anything related to Anuradhapura (අනුරාධපුර / அனுராதபுரம்).

[Travellers' Guide To Anuradhapura | Wikitravel](https://wikitravel.org/en/Anuradhapura)
##Rules
1. Follow [reddiquette.](/help/reddiquette)

2. Please link to images directly. Direct links make browsing easier for those using RES or through a mobile device.

3. Please do not post or request personal information, yours or others. Real or fake.

4. Harassment of others is strictly forbidden. We will not tolerate any kind of incitement to action against anyone. Keep comments civil and be respectful of your fellow users.

5. Please be sure to correctly mark NSFW content after submitting.
